OL,3,CHow a teenager who died of cancer is
OL,4,Cstill helping hundreds of other
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FA Bath teenager who died of cancer is
OL,8,Fstill helping hundreds of other
OL,9,Ffamilies affected by the disease.
OL,11,FBen Saunders passed away, aged 18,
OL,12,Ffrom a synovial sarcoma attached to
OL,13,Fhis heart on 25 August 2020.
OL,15,FSince then, the Ben Saunders
OL,16,FFoundation - which he started himself
OL,17,F- has raised more than #750,000 and
OL,18,Fhelped 350 families impacted by cancer.
