OL,3,CHow a teenager who died of cancer is
OL,4,Cstill helping hundreds of other
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FSpeaking on the fourth anniversary of
OL,8,Fhis death, Ben's father Tom said: "Ben
OL,9,Fwas a confident young man, very
OL,10,Fhandsome and extremely popular.
OL,12,F"It the final few weeks of his life,
OL,13,Fthe foundation was all he thought
OL,14,Fabout.
OL,16,F"He wouldn't have believed how well
OL,17,Fthe foundation has grown, but he would
OL,18,Fbe very proud of it."
