OL,3,CHow a teenager who died of cancer is
OL,4,Cstill helping hundreds of other
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FBefore he passed away, Ben raised
OL,8,Fnearly #40,000 to buy a lodge in the
OL,9,FCotswolds that other families going
OL,10,Fthrough cancer could enjoy.
OL,12,FThey have the chance to try water
OL,13,Fsports, crazy golf, indoor and outdoor
OL,14,Fswimming pools - or just take a much-
OL,15,Fneeded break.
OL,17,FThe charity now owns two lodges, which
OL,18,Fit funds through a monthly prize draw
OL,19,Fand the Bath Half Marathon every year.
