OL,3,CHow a teenager who died of cancer is
OL,4,Cstill helping hundreds of other
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FTom, the foundation chairman, said:
OL,8,F"The feedback is simply incredible,
OL,9,Fwe've had families stay from all over
OL,10,FEngland, Wales and the North of
OL,11,FScotland, during the school holidays
OL,12,Fif we had five holiday homes we could
OL,13,Feasily fill them.
OL,15,F"This is an horrendous time of the
OL,16,Fyear for our family with Ben's
OL,17,Fanniversary this weekend, we are
OL,18,Fhowever very proud of everything that
OL,19,Fhas been achieved to full fill his
OL,20,Flast wish that was never to be
OL,21,Fforgotten".
